/* Stock-engine symbols the m4a TU (lib/m4a/m4a.o) references but the alias
   generator sources don't name. Mixer fns + CpuSet resolve to their kept
   asm Func_<addr>; gMaxLines/gNumMusicPlayers are symbol-as-value config;
   SoundMainRAM_Buffer is the IWRAM mixer-code buffer. */
